#Python Stuff
.venv/*

# Eclipse/Momentics metadata (local)
**/.cproject
**/.project

# --- QNX Build Artifacts ---
# Ignores the 'obj' folder created by our Makefile
**/obj/

# Common build output folders
**/build/

# Ignore built executables in QNX_files/
QNX_files/main
QNX_files/main_supervisor
QNX_files/watchdog
QNX_files/braking_system
QNX_files/telemetry_system
QNX_files/client
QNX_files/driving_system

# Ignores common QNX/Momentics architecture-specific output folders
**/armle-v7*/
**/aarch64*/
**/x86_64*/
**/o.*/

# --- IDE Metadata ---
# We keep .project and .cproject, but ignore the local user settings
**/.settings/
**/.externalToolBuilders/

# --- General C/C++ Junk ---
*.o
*.so
*.a
*.tmp
.DS_Store
